snippet.title: Peak Conquest | Season 7 Cinematic Trailer - Arena Breakout
snippet.description:
Hecate, master of shadow operations, is ready to take the battlefield by storm.  With her cunning and deadly precision, she's more than just a force to be reckoned with — she's a legend in the making.
The full experience will be available in Season 7 on iOS and Android! http://bit.ly/3Jel2aJ
